rows.label: qst103303_msg0001
rows.name: Whazzat?

rows.label: qst103303_msg0002
rows.name: From big bro?

rows.label: qst103303_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh, cool!
It's not just money for a change!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0004
rows.name: Lemme see, lemme see!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0005
rows.name: Thanks for bringing it to us!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0006
rows.name:
Ever since our big bro became a Driver,
we've been eating our fill!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0007
rows.name: Drivers are super cool!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0008
rows.name: If only Da hadn't had to leave...

rows.label: qst103303_msg0009
rows.name:
Those Superbian dummies didn't
make Ma better, either...

rows.label: qst103303_msg0010
rows.name:
But at least they made our bro
a Driver!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0011
rows.name: Ma... *sniff*

rows.label: qst103303_msg0012
rows.name:
Morca!
You promised you wouldn't cry
for Ma anymore.

rows.label: qst103303_msg0013
rows.name:
Oh, yeah... Gotta be strong.
Sorry, Neel...

rows.label: qst103303_msg0014
rows.name:
After Ma passed away,
Da just took off.

rows.label: qst103303_msg0015
rows.name:
That was when our bro decided
to see if he could become a Driver.

rows.label: qst103303_msg0016
rows.name:
I'm gonna be a Driver too!
Then I can help out Big Bro!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0017
rows.name:
Me too, me too! I'd love to have
one of those animal Blades!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0018
rows.name:
Hey, you two.
Thank the nice people properly.

rows.label: qst103303_msg0019
rows.name:
Thank you for
all the neat stuff!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0020
rows.name: Thanks!

rows.label: qst103303_msg0021
rows.name:
If you see our brother again,
please tell him we're doing good.

rows.label: qst103303_msg0022
rows.name: Thanks again!
